    "ChatGPT produced two additional strategies, namely a table and a picture, each containing one correct response.",
    "Unfortunately, as shown in Figure 10, ChatGPT misinterpreted the table and incorrectly reported the total number of legs for 17 lions and 12 water birds as 88.",
    "While ChatGPT provided a correct response using pictures, the image generated was in JavaScript, as depicted in Figure 11, which may be challenging to comprehend and require an additional application to produce an accurate image.",
